.SH NAME
XkbKeyGroupInfo \- Returns tha number of crewz of symbols bound ta tha key 
correspondin ta 
keycode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.HP
.B unsigned char XkbKeyGroupInfo
.BI "(\^XkbDescPtr " "xkb" "\^,"
.BI "KeyCode " "keycode" "\^);"
.if n .ti +5n
.if t .ti +.5i
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
.I \- xkb
Xkb description of interest
